---
Checks:          'clang-diagnostic-*,clang-analyzer-*,-fuchsia-*,-cppcoreguidelines-pro-bounds-array-to-pointer-decay,-google-build-using-namespace,-hicpp-no-array-decay,-modernize-use-trailing-return-type,-hicpp-braces-around-statements,-cppcoreguidelines-pro-bounds-pointer-arithmetic,-llvm-header-guard,-google-global-names-in-headers,-cppcoreguidelines-special-member-functions,-hicpp-special-member-functions,-cppcoreguidelines-owning-memory,-cppcoreguidelines-pro-bounds-constant-array-index'
